  "original_query": "[Chat History Summary] Хэрэглэгч Хэпийн ангилалтай зээлүүдийг хайж байна.  [Previous SQL (for reference - use exact column names and values from this)]: ```sql SELECT     acnt_code,     customer_name,     acnt_name,     class_name,     principal,     cur_code,     status,     txn_date FROM dbm.loan_balance_detail WHERE     txn_date = (SELECT MAX(txn_date) FROM dbm.loan_balance_detail)     AND status = 'O'     AND principal > 0     AND class_name = 'ХЭВИЙН' ORDER BY principal DESC; ```  [Current Question] Зээлдэгчдээр нь харуул",
